data.name: lblSexActInstruct.Text
data.value: 0-5 -> Low Risk - Place patient on routine 15 minute checks. 6-9 -> Moderate Risk - Place patient on routine 15 minute checks and monitor. 10+ -> High Risk - Patient to be placed on sexual acting out precautions, identify risk to treatment team, on red sheet and chart.
